channel.title: Paying $5 for cache help
channel.description:
You come on TV with me and help fix my Cache.
Basically the first time you run it, it makes the folder but then gives errors. Close it, run it again, it downloads the cache and then either gets to about 40% and thinks its done, so it's starts unpacking but the cache is corrupt so it screws up OR it gets to 100% and gives a 3D like image.
